---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for Zelnot technology consulting services.">
  <section class="bg-slate-50 section-padding">
    <div class="container-tight">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Information I Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
          When you submit a contact form on this website, I collect the information you provide:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-600 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Company name (optional)</li>
          <li>Message content</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">How I Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
          Information collected through contact forms is used solely to respond to your inquiry. 
          Your data is never sold, rented, or shared with third parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Form Submissions</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
          Contact form submissions are processed through Formspree, a third-party form service. 
          Your submission data is sent to Formspree to deliver the message to my email.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
          Contact form submissions are retained for up to 6 months for reference and follow-up purposes.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
          You have the right to request deletion of any personal data I've collected. 
          Contact me at zelnot@zelnot.com to make such a request.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600">
          For privacy-related questions, contact me at <a href="mailto:zelnot@zelnot.com" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700">zelnot@zelnot.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
